<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sink-vi">sink <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪŋk/    美 /sɪŋk/  </p>
<p>(sank, sunk)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-float">1.★ <strong>(船等) 下沉  反 float；(日、月) 下落：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship <strong>sank to the bottom of</strong> the river.
船沉入了河底。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun was starting to sink.
太阳开始下山。</p><footer>2010 浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(头、目光等) 下垂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His head sank on his chest.
他的头垂在胸前。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>坐下；倒下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She let out a sigh and <strong>sank into a</strong> chair.
她叹息了一声，颓然坐进椅子里。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>消沉；陷入：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Her heart sank</strong> as the list ended without her name.
名单读完却没听到自己的名字，她心里一沉。</p><footer>2008 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>was</strong> worried and <strong>sank in</strong> my thoughts.
我有些担心，陷入了深思。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Fred entered without knocking and, very out of breath, sank <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ a chair.  （2008 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. into  </p></div>